name: SamDoesArts Embedding #1
description:
Trained in 1.5!!

This is one of my two SamDoesArts embeddings.

You have to invoke the Embedding using its name

you can also use (<SamDoesArt1>:0.84) to adjust the weight

Im adding them in separte uploads because i might do further testing on each one.

This should work in multiple models
